parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbags did not deploy in a crash
resulting in injuries or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The Takata airbag recall has led to a prolonged and frustrating experience for many owners, leaving them with a sense of uncertainty and insecurity.
symptoms: Owners have experienced difficulties in getting their vehicles repaired
including unavailability of parts
lack of communication from dealerships and manufacturers
and excessive wait times.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The airbag light illumination can indicate a potential problem with the airbag system, which can lead to a failure to deploy in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Airbag light is illuminated on the dashboard
indicating a problem with the airbag system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power sliding door can cause the door to open or close unexpectedly, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially if children or pets are in the vehicle.
symptoms: The power sliding door opens or closes unexpectedly
the door does not latch properly
the door makes abnormal noises
the door cable breaks or frays
the door motor fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in repairing the power sliding door failure can lead to continued risk of accidents, injuries, or fatalities, as well as frustration and inconvenience for vehicle owners.
symptoms: The parts to repair the power sliding door failure are unavailable
the manufacturer exceeds a reasonable amount of time for the recall repair
the dealer is unable to provide a repair remedy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or experience intermittent issues with various systems, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The dashboard lights flash
the vehicle turns off
the battery light comes on
the vehicle stalls
the speedometer and gas gauge do not work
the brake system malfunctions
and the ABS and VSC warning lights come on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power sliding doors can cause the doors to open or close unexpectedly, which can lead to accidents or injuries, especially when children are involved.
symptoms: The power sliding doors do not latch or close properly
the doors open or close unexpectedly
the door ajar light and warning bells sound frequently
and the doors cannot be secured.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the sunroof can cause it to get stuck in the open position, which can lead to water damage, noise, and distraction while driving.
symptoms: The sunroof gets stuck in the open position and will not close.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The poor dashboard illumination can cause difficulty in reading the dashboard instruments, especially during daytime driving, which can lead to accidents or errors.
symptoms: The dashboard is not well-lit
especially during daytime driving
and the dashboard instruments are difficult to read.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the intermittent wiper can cause reduced visibility during rainy or snowy conditions, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The intermittent wiper is reversed
with the slow setting running fast and the fast setting running slow.
